{
    "poem_title": "Le Mendiant",
    "author": "Germain Nouveau",
    "structure": "suite périodique",
    "year": "1922",
    "manually_checked": false,
    "stanzas": [
        {
            "stanza_number": 1,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 1,
                    "line_text": "L’être que j’adore en ce monde,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 2,
                    "line_text": "Eût-il les pieds noirs et des poux,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 3,
                    "line_text": "C’est le mendiant, il m’inonde",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 4,
                    "line_text": "Le cœur d’une extase profonde ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 5,
                    "line_text": "Je lui baiserais les genoux.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "L’être que j’adore en ce monde,\nEût-il les pieds noirs et des poux,\nC’est le mendiant, il m’inonde\nLe cœur d’une extase profonde ;\nJe lui baiserais les genoux."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 2,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 6,
                    "line_text": "D’abord il convient de vous dire",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 7,
                    "line_text": "Que si je ne l’adorais pas,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 8,
                    "line_text": "Ça ferait peut-être sourire ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 9,
                    "line_text": "On penserait : Hé ! le bon sire !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 10,
                    "line_text": "Il a le « trac » pour ses ducats.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "D’abord il convient de vous dire\nQue si je ne l’adorais pas,\nÇa ferait peut-être sourire ;\nOn penserait : Hé ! le bon sire !\nIl a le « trac » pour ses ducats."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 3,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 11,
                    "line_text": "Il a peur de faire l’aumône,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 12,
                    "line_text": "Ou qu’on le vole, il a raison",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 13,
                    "line_text": "Dans la vie, ah ! tout n’est pas jaune,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 14,
                    "line_text": "Et mon ami le plus béjaune",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 15,
                    "line_text": "Ne viendrait pas à la maison.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Il a peur de faire l’aumône,\nOu qu’on le vole, il a raison\nDans la vie, ah ! tout n’est pas jaune,\nEt mon ami le plus béjaune\nNe viendrait pas à la maison."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 4,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 16,
                    "line_text": "Ou, s’il venait, il voudrait faire,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 17,
                    "line_text": "Tout comme moi, les mêmes frais,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 18,
                    "line_text": "Nous compterions, quelle misère !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 19,
                    "line_text": "Et s’il me cassait, quoi ? son verre ?",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 20,
                    "line_text": "Ah ! la tête que je ferais !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Ou, s’il venait, il voudrait faire,\nTout comme moi, les mêmes frais,\nNous compterions, quelle misère !\nEt s’il me cassait, quoi ? son verre ?\nAh ! la tête que je ferais !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 5,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 21,
                    "line_text": "Je parlerais de ma famille",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 22,
                    "line_text": "Tant, que c’en serait Han-Mer-Dent :",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 23,
                    "line_text": "« J’ai ma femme, mon fils, ma fille ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 24,
                    "line_text": "Oui, la petite est très gentille,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 25,
                    "line_text": "Mais ça coûte. — C’est évident ! »",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Je parlerais de ma famille\nTant, que c’en serait Han-Mer-Dent :\n« J’ai ma femme, mon fils, ma fille ;\nOui, la petite est très gentille,\nMais ça coûte. — C’est évident ! »"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 6,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 26,
                    "line_text": "Le mendiant, qu’est-ce qu’il coûte ?",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 27,
                    "line_text": "Titus disait : un heureux jour.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 28,
                    "line_text": "Quand nous verrons plus d’une goutte,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 29,
                    "line_text": "Chacun trouvera sur sa route",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 30,
                    "line_text": "Qu’avec cet homme, on fait l’amour.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Le mendiant, qu’est-ce qu’il coûte ?\nTitus disait : un heureux jour.\nQuand nous verrons plus d’une goutte,\nChacun trouvera sur sa route\nQu’avec cet homme, on fait l’amour."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 7,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 31,
                    "line_text": "Je l’aime, comme une parente,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 32,
                    "line_text": "Pauvre… mais ça… c’est un détail…,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 33,
                    "line_text": "D’une façon bien différente.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 34,
                    "line_text": "Si j’avais mille francs de rente.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 35,
                    "line_text": "Je lui donnerais… du travail.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Je l’aime, comme une parente,\nPauvre… mais ça… c’est un détail…,\nD’une façon bien différente.\nSi j’avais mille francs de rente.\nJe lui donnerais… du travail."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 8,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 36,
                    "line_text": "Je lui dirais : Tu vas me faire",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 37,
                    "line_text": "Un bonhomme sur ce papier.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 38,
                    "line_text": "— « Monsieur, je ne dessine guère, »",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 39,
                    "line_text": "Alors… de me foutre en colère,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 40,
                    "line_text": "Trouves-tu cela trop… pompier ?",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Je lui dirais : Tu vas me faire\nUn bonhomme sur ce papier.\n— « Monsieur, je ne dessine guère, »\nAlors… de me foutre en colère,\nTrouves-tu cela trop… pompier ?"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 9,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 41,
                    "line_text": "Il dessinerait son bonhomme",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 42,
                    "line_text": "Bien ou mal, naturellement.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 43,
                    "line_text": "Je dirais : Combien ? — « Telle somme. »",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 44,
                    "line_text": "Et je paierais ; c’est presque, en somme,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 45,
                    "line_text": "Ce que fait le Gouvernement.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Il dessinerait son bonhomme\nBien ou mal, naturellement.\nJe dirais : Combien ? — « Telle somme. »\nEt je paierais ; c’est presque, en somme,\nCe que fait le Gouvernement."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 10,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 46,
                    "line_text": "Le mendiant, mais c’est mon frère !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 47,
                    "line_text": "Comment, mon frère ? Mais, c’est moi.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 48,
                    "line_text": "Je commence par me la faire,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 49,
                    "line_text": "La charité, la chose est claire.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 50,
                    "line_text": "Tu te la fais aussi, va, Toi.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Le mendiant, mais c’est mon frère !\nComment, mon frère ? Mais, c’est moi.\nJe commence par me la faire,\nLa charité, la chose est claire.\nTu te la fais aussi, va, Toi."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 11,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 51,
                    "line_text": "Moi, souvent « je me le demande »",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 52,
                    "line_text": "Et demande, quand ça me plaît.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 53,
                    "line_text": "Et bien ! pour ma langue gourmande,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 54,
                    "line_text": "Plus que la vôtre n’est normande,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 55,
                    "line_text": "Si saint Pierre ouvrait son volet",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Moi, souvent « je me le demande »\nEt demande, quand ça me plaît.\nEt bien ! pour ma langue gourmande,\nPlus que la vôtre n’est normande,\nSi saint Pierre ouvrait son volet"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 12,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 56,
                    "line_text": "Seulement pour une seconde :",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 57,
                    "line_text": "Si je suis là, si je le vois,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 58,
                    "line_text": "Bien que je doute qu’il réponde,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 59,
                    "line_text": "Je lui demande la plus ronde",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 60,
                    "line_text": "Des lunes qui rient dans les bois.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Seulement pour une seconde :\nSi je suis là, si je le vois,\nBien que je doute qu’il réponde,\nJe lui demande la plus ronde\nDes lunes qui rient dans les bois."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 13,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 61,
                    "line_text": "Et si, — surprise ! et joie extrême ! —",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 62,
                    "line_text": "J’entends : « tiens ! enfant, la voici ! »",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 63,
                    "line_text": "Comme avec tes baisers que j’aime,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 64,
                    "line_text": "Je me barbouille tout de crème,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 65,
                    "line_text": "Sans seulement dire : merci.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Et si, — surprise ! et joie extrême ! —\nJ’entends : « tiens ! enfant, la voici ! »\nComme avec tes baisers que j’aime,\nJe me barbouille tout de crème,\nSans seulement dire : merci."
        }
